evals.prompt:
Convert this legacy AutoPilot script to SA Pro C#:

_GN_' Remove positions with zero capacity and log removed UPCs
_GN_Open output file {FileName="C:\Reports\removed_products.txt"}
_GN_Write to file {Text="Removed Products Report"}
_PS_Open project file {FileName="C:\Planograms\Sample.psa"}
_PS_For planograms
  _PS_For positions
    _GN_If GetValue("Position","Capacity")=0 Then
      _GN_Write to file {Text=GetValue("Position","UPC")}
      _PS_Delete position {Option="CurrentPosition"}
    _GN_End if
  _PS_End positions
_PS_End planograms
_PS_Save project file
_PS_Close project file
_GN_Close output file
